window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>As the summer solstice nears and hordes of demons prepare to cross the veil, Max and his faithful crew race to unite the kingdoms for the coming battle.</b></p> <p>But when dark forces strike the earth and water elementals, threatening the annihilation of all life, Max faces an impossible task. Only he can enter the elemental realms to save themâ€”but how can one man be everywhere at once?</p> <p>Can Max find a solution in time to save the kingdoms?</p> <p><i>In </i>Elemental<i>, book five of the Giseria Chronicles, Max's dreams of a quiet life slip further away as he fights to prevent extinction. Narrated in duet style.</i></p>"; 
